      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so im a student in berlin and things are getting pretty stressful with finals coming up. i've been taking sertraline for my depression but i feel like it isn't quite doing enough to help with my mood lately. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to my routine since it's natural and should help boost my serotonin, is it cool to take them together?",
