    "summary": "The user is asking for validation to combine Sertraline (an SSRI) with St. John's Wort (a herbal supplement) to manage exam stress, despite being warned of risks. The assistant consistently refuses to validate the user's desire to self-medicate, correctly identifying the risk of interaction and repeatedly advising consultation with a healthcare professional.",
